	   <tr><td colspan=2>At level 50 every 1 point of int or wis gives you 10 mana.&nbsp;&nbsp;This item at level 50 is the equivalent of 4.5 int.  I believe the rule now is that you can have 10 mana per 1 int/wis all the way up to 255 int/wis.  If that is a true fact then it will be pretty easy to determine which items are better based on stat bonus vs. +mana.<br><br>Cone of mystics and Stein of Moggok would be 2 cheap yet powerful caster items at level 50.... provided you can't get something more uber :).... this thing would be good to twink a level 1 for the tasty mana it would give :)<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Roanin Tsunamii<br>Disciple of Aiaka :)</td></tr>
