	   <tr><td colspan=2>One int does equal 10 mana at 50, before the 200 cap.&nbsp;&nbsp;However after 200 the bonus is cut in half, so at 50th you get 5 mana per int.  At 60th it's 12/6.  Now keeping this in mind, most of the time 10mana is worth more than 1int.  You can get to the 200 soft cap pretty easy, so try for mana gear over int gear and it'll pay off in the long run.<br>&nbsp;<br>Phelon Lvl 57 Necro<br>Morell Thule<br><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=390038 target=_new>Magelo Profile</a><br>Master of many alts</td></tr>
